  - `missing_info` or `problem`: Describe what's missing or wrong (be specific)
  - `suggestion`: How to fix it. Write as if you are the reader giving feedback in first person. Explain why the information matters to you - the compressor doesn't have access to your full reading intent, so help them understand what you care about and why.

